  05 Apr 2007; Fabian Groffen <fabian@gentoo.org> aix/make.defaults,
  darwin/make.defaults, irix/make.defaults, linux/make.defaults,
  +package.provided, sunos/make.defaults:
  Add nostip to non-Linux profiles because they don't have scanelf. Added
  package.provided for sys-apps/shadow.

  04 Apr 2007; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> aix/use.mask,
  darwin/use.mask, sunos/use.mask, +use.mask:
  Moved elibc/kernel/userland USE-flags masking to the default-prefix profile,
  and unmasked them in the specific profiles again

  04 Apr 2007; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org>:
  Depend on the base profile, just only change the defaults when required

